metadata.name: Top On Press Events
metadata.description: HPX Events Model with IIDE Table

datasets.name: paas_tracking_card_metrics
datasets.query: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('day', session_start_date_time) AS day_event_date_time, app_name AS control, SUM(total_device_count) AS total_clicks FROM team_css_analytics_prod.hpx_analytics.paas_tracking_card_metrics WHERE session_start_date_time >= '2023-05-01' AND app_name NOT LIKE '%testid%' AND app_name != 'welcome core navigationviewitem id' GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('day', session_start_date_time), app_name ORDER BY day_event_date_time, total_clicks DESC

frame.title: Top On Press Events Over Time
